Use the standard library
This is how to sorted_list_sum of lst:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 0

   Do this lst's length times:
      Remember that word is item i in lst
      When remainder of (word's length) and 2 is 0, then:
         Add result to word
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   Remember that n is result's length
   Do this n times:
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this diff of n and 1 times:
         When j is at least diff of n and 1, then:
            Leave the loop
         End when
         Remember that a is item j in result
         Remember that b is item (sum of j and 1) in result
         When a's length is more than b's length, then:
            Remember that item j in result is b
            Remember that item (sum of j and 1) in result is a
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
   End do

   The answer is result
Now you know